title: Adi Kapyare Koottamani
subTitle: Lakshmi, hoping to enter and exit the college hostel unnoticed, offers Bhanuprasad, a student, a sum of money. However, she ends up trapped in the building due to a series of chaotic events.

title: Sallapam
subTitle: Radha and Sasikumar fall in love with each other. However, her life takes a turn when he refuses to marry her because of his family problems.

title: Maniyarayile Ashokan
subTitle: Ashokan desperately wishes to get married as he is past the marriageable age. However, bad luck and a series of unfortunate circumstances threaten to make this a distant dream.

title: Nanma
subTitle: For a living, Muthu extracts and disposes of corpses from rivers. Unknown to Muthu, his son becomes a henchman for a moneylender as he wants his father to have a respectable job.

title: Mambazhakkalam
subTitle: When his father dies, Chandran is forced to go abroad to earn money to pay his father's dues. On a holiday to India, he meets his childhood lover and hopes to rekindle the relationship.

title: Bheeshmaparvam
subTitle: Michael, the third son of the Anjootti family in Kochi, takes over the business. Moreover, few house members join with foes to clamp down on him.

title: Karyasthan
subTitle: After a past incident, two powerful clans of Krishnapuram remain estranged until one day, a man with a mysterious past decides to bring the families together.

title: Thanneermathan Dinangal
subTitle: Jaison, a teenager, has a crush on Keerthy, but she does not reciprocate his feelings. To make things worse, he gets in trouble with Ravi, the new teacher who is liked by everyone, especially Keerthy.

title: RDX
subTitle: Robert, Dony and Xavier grow up together while honing their fighting skills. However, after an incident separates them for several years, an attack on their family reunites the three friends.

title: Nagaravaridhi Naduvil Njan
subTitle: As Venu's dream is to secure an MBBS admission for his daughter, he decides to sell his property to get money for her education. However, his family members try to disrupt his plans.

title: Nagaravaridhi Naduvil Njan
subTitle: As Venu's dream is to secure an MBBS admission for his daughter, he decides to sell his property to get money for her education. However, his family members try to disrupt his plans.

title: Samastha keralam P O
subTitle: Prabhakaran, a Gandhian panchayat member, fights corruption in Thonnurkara village. However, his crusade for people's welfare angers corrupt politicians.

title: Oru Kaatil Oru Paykappal
subTitle: When Sara's homestay receives Ajith as a guest, he falls for her. However, unbeknownst to him, Sara's father arranges for her to marry a rich man.

title: Corona Papers
subTitle: Rahul, a young police officer, loses his service revolver, triggering chaos as a bank robbery and a string of crimes become linked to the missing weapon.

title: Nadodimannan
subTitle: Padmanabhan, a man who joins political rallies to make money, gets into trouble when he is elected mayor of Thiruvananthapuram and is forced to fight corruption in the city.

title: One
subTitle: An aspiring policeman embarks on an unauthorised mission to investigate a devious scientist. However, he confronts various challenges when his actions are exposed.

title: Vettam
subTitle: Gopalakrishnan meets Veena while trying to smuggle a stolen necklace. Later, he accompanies Veena on her mission to unite with her lover.

title: Swapnakoodu
subTitle: Three men compete against each other to win the affections of a beautiful woman. However, complications arise when her mother suffers from a heart attack.

title: Avatharam
subTitle: Kuppaswamy, an innocent theatre enthusiast, falls in love with visually challenged Ponnama after joining a troupe. When the troupe struggles financially, the couple moves to the city.

title: Minnal Murali
subTitle: Jaison, a young tailor, gains superpowers after being struck by lightning. However, he must thwart the evil intentions of an unexpected adversary to become the superhero that his rural village needs.

title: Minnal Murali
subTitle: Jaison, a young tailor, gains superpowers after being struck by lightning. However, he must thwart the evil intentions of an unexpected adversary to become the superhero that his rural village needs.

title: Highway Police
subTitle: United by tragedy, Mammud and Inspector Jayachandran forge an alliance to dismantle a powerful crime syndicate, combining their quest for justice with personal vendettas.

title: Cheriya Kallanum Valiya Poleesum
subTitle: Sadasivan comes across a house where the owner, Kumaran, has committed suicide to protect his wife, Soumini. However, what is even stranger is that a man who is visually challenged is always around.

title: Balram vs. Tharadas
subTitle: When Balram seizes a cache of arms and ammunition, his investigations lead him to a criminal, Tharadas. However, it is not easy for Balram to catch Tharadas until he involves his girlfriend.

title: Niram
subTitle: Aby realises that he is in love with Sona, his childhood friend, but is unable to express his feelings. However, he faces a dilemma when he learns that her marriage has already been arranged.

title: Premam
subTitle: Vikram falls in love with different women at various stages of his life and with each experience, he bears the pain and emotions of separation.

title: Bangalore Days
subTitle: Three cousins, Divya, Krishnan and Arjuna, share a close bond and decide to move to Bangalore to fulfil their childhood dreams. There, they face challenges that will change their lives forever.

title: June
subTitle: June, a teenager, believes that there is nothing remarkable about her. She experiences adolescent crushes, handles heartbreaks and fights insecurities as she grows into a mature and confident woman.

title: Hridayam
subTitle: Arun, a young man, enrols in an engineering college but falls prey to bad habits. As he grows up, he decides to turn over a new leaf and become a responsible adult.

title: Classmates
subTitle: A group of college friends meet after many years for a class reunion. However, due to some unexpected turn of events, several dark secrets are revealed, which changes their lives.
